    "## Data Quality Checks (EDA)\n",
    "\n",
    "We check:\n",
    "- Missing values\n",
    "- Duplicate rows\n",
    "\n",
    "Duplicates (if any) are removed to prevent repeated samples affecting training/evaluation."
