  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "source": [
    "## Label Transformation (Regrouping)\n",
    "\n",
    "The original integer quality score is regrouped into three classes:\n",
    "- Low (≤5), Medium (=6), High (≥7)\n",
    "\n",
    "Rationale:\n",
    "- Improves interpretability and stabilises classification.\n",
    "- Reduces sensitivity to small rating differences in subjective quality scores."
   ],
   "metadata": {
    "id": "9z7hpFdtqGW4"
   }
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "source": [
    "def regroup_quality(q: int) -> str:\n    if q <= 5:\n        return \"Low\"\n    elif q == 6:\n        return \"Medium\"\n    else:\n        return \"High\"\n\ndf[\"quality_label\"] = df[\"quality\"].apply(regroup_quality)\n\nprint(\"Original quality distribution:\")\nprint(df[\"quality\"].value_counts().sort_index())\n\nprint(\"\\nRegrouped label distribution:\")\nprint(df[\"quality_label\"].value_counts())\n\n"
   ],
   "metadata": {
    "colab": {
     "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
    },
    "id": "d37JwQ5o7dnR",
    "outputId": "8bd8ebeb-5d09-49e4-d554-27c35396cce0"
   },
   "execution_count": 30,
