    "## Train/Test Split\n",
    "\n",
    "We keep 20% as a held-out test set for final evaluation only.\n",
    "The training set is used for cross-validation and GridSearchCV tuning.\n",
    "\n",
    "Stratification preserves class proportions."
   ],
   "metadata": {
    "id": "vM1PPs0oWe3Q"
   }
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "source": [
    "X = df.drop(columns=[\"quality\", \"quality_label\"])\ny = df[\"quality_label\"]\n\nX_train, X_test, y_train, y_test = train_test_split(\n    X, y,\n    test_size=0.2,\n    stratify=y,\n    random_state=42\n)\n\nprint(\"Train shape:\", X_train.shape, y_train.shape)\nprint(\"Test shape: \", X_test.shape, y_test.shape)\n"
   ],
   "metadata": {
